			Company Description 
		


                Harmony Gold Mining Co. Ltd. engages in gold mining and exploration activities. The firm's operations are located in South Africa and Papua New Guinea. The company was founded on August 25, 1950 and is headquartered in Randfontein, South Africa.
            




